com.lightbend.lagom.javadsl.server

Interface LagomServiceRouter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    play.api.routing.Router

    public interface LagomServiceRouter
extends play.api.routing.Router
    A Lagom service router. This interface doesn't add anything, except that it makes the router created by the LagomServer strongly typed. This allows it to be dependency injected by type, making it simple to use it in combination with the Play routes file. For example, if using a custom router, the Lagom router could be routed to from the routes file like this: 
     ->   /     com.lightbend.lagom.javadsl.server.LagomServiceRouter
